TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi beforefieldinit ConsumptionModernUsageDetail extends Azure.ResourceManager.Consumption.Models.ConsumptionUsageDetail

Docs.summary: Modern usage detail.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property AdditionalInfo As String

Docs.summary: Additional details of this usage item. Use this field to get usage line item specific details such as the actual VM Size (ServiceType) or the ratio in which the reservation discount is applied.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property BenefitId As String

Docs.summary: Unique identifier for the applicable benefit.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property BenefitName As String

Docs.summary: Name of the applicable benefit.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property BillingAccountId As String

Docs.summary: Billing Account identifier.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property BillingAccountName As String

Docs.summary: Name of the Billing Account.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property BillingCurrencyCode As String

Docs.summary: The currency defining the billed cost.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property BillingPeriodEndOn As Nullable(Of DateTimeOffset)

Docs.summary: Billing Period End Date as in the invoice.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property BillingPeriodStartOn As Nullable(Of DateTimeOffset)

Docs.summary: Billing Period Start Date as in the invoice.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property BillingProfileId As String

Docs.summary: Identifier for the billing profile that groups costs across invoices in the a singular billing currency across across the customers who have onboarded the Microsoft customer agreement and the customers in CSP who have made entitlement purchases like SaaS, Marketplace, RI, etc.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property BillingProfileName As String

Docs.summary: Name of the billing profile that groups costs across invoices in the a singular billing currency across across the customers who have onboarded the Microsoft customer agreement and the customers in CSP who have made entitlement purchases like SaaS, Marketplace, RI, etc.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ChargeType As String

Docs.summary: Indicates a charge represents credits, usage, a Marketplace purchase, a reservation fee, or a refund.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ConsumedService As String

Docs.summary: Consumed service name. Name of the azure resource provider that emits the usage or was purchased. This value is not provided for marketplace usage.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property CostAllocationRuleName As String

Docs.summary: Name for Cost Allocation Rule.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property CostCenter As String

Docs.summary: The cost center of this department if it is a department and a cost center is provided.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property CostInBillingCurrency As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: ExtendedCost or blended cost before tax in billed currency.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property CostInPricingCurrency As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: ExtendedCost or blended cost before tax in pricing currency to correlate with prices.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property CostInUSD As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: Estimated extendedCost or blended cost before tax in USD.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property CustomerName As String

Docs.summary: Name of the customer's AAD tenant.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property CustomerTenantId As String

Docs.summary: Identifier of the customer's AAD tenant.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property EffectivePrice As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: Effective Price that's charged for the usage.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ExchangeRate As String

Docs.summary: Exchange rate used in conversion from pricing currency to billing currency.

Docs.summary: Date on which exchange rate used in conversion from pricing currency to billing currency.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ExchangeRatePricingToBilling As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: Exchange Rate from pricing currency to billing currency.

Docs.summary: Indicates how frequently this charge will occur. OneTime for purchases which only happen once, Monthly for fees which recur every month, and UsageBased for charges based on how much a service is used.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property InstanceName As String

Docs.summary: Instance Name.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property InvoiceId As String

Docs.summary: Invoice ID as on the invoice where the specific transaction appears.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property InvoiceSectionId As String

Docs.summary: Identifier of the project that is being charged in the invoice. Not applicable for Microsoft Customer Agreements onboarded by partners.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property InvoiceSectionName As String

Docs.summary: Name of the project that is being charged in the invoice. Not applicable for Microsoft Customer Agreements onboarded by partners.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property IsAzureCreditEligible As Nullable(Of Boolean)

Docs.summary: Determines if the cost is eligible to be paid for using Azure credits.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property MarketPrice As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: Market Price that's charged for the usage.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property MeterCategory As String

Docs.summary: Identifies the top-level service for the usage.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property MeterId As Nullable(Of Guid)

Docs.summary: The meter id (GUID). Not available for marketplace. For reserved instance this represents the primary meter for which the reservation was purchased. For the actual VM Size for which the reservation is purchased see productOrderName.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property MeterName As String

Docs.summary: Identifies the name of the meter against which consumption is measured.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property MeterRegion As String

Docs.summary: Identifies the location of the datacenter for certain services that are priced based on datacenter location.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property MeterSubCategory As String

Docs.summary: Defines the type or sub-category of Azure service that can affect the rate.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property On As Nullable(Of DateTimeOffset)

Docs.summary: Date for the usage record.

Docs.summary: Flag to indicate if partner earned credit has been applied or not.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PartnerEarnedCreditRate As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: Rate of discount applied if there is a partner earned credit (PEC) based on partner admin link access.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PartnerName As String

Docs.summary: Name of the partner' AAD tenant.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PartnerTenantId As String

Docs.summary: Identifier for the partner's AAD tenant.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PaygCostInBillingCurrency As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: The amount of PayG cost before tax in billing currency.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PaygCostInUSD As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: The amount of PayG cost before tax in US Dollar currency.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PayGPrice As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: Retail price for the resource.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PreviousInvoiceId As String

Docs.summary: Reference to an original invoice there is a refund (negative cost). This is populated only when there is a refund.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PricingCurrencyCode As String

Docs.summary: Pricing Billing Currency.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PricingModel As Nullable(Of ConsumptionPricingModelType)

Docs.summary: Identifier that indicates how the meter is priced.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property Product As String

Docs.summary: Name of the product that has accrued charges by consumption or purchase as listed in the invoice. Not available for Marketplace.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ProductIdentifier As String

Docs.summary: Identifier for the product that has accrued charges by consumption or purchase . This is the concatenated key of productId and SkuId in partner center.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ProductOrderId As String

Docs.summary: The identifier for the asset or Azure plan name that the subscription belongs to. For example: Azure Plan. For reservations this is the Reservation Order ID.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ProductOrderName As String

Docs.summary: Product Order Name. For reservations this is the SKU that was purchased.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property Provider As String

Docs.summary: Identifier for Product Category or Line Of Business, Ex - Azure, Microsoft 365, AWS e.t.c.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PublisherId As String

Docs.summary: Publisher Id.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PublisherName As String

Docs.summary: Name of the publisher of the service including Microsoft or Third Party publishers.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property PublisherType As String

Docs.summary: Type of publisher that identifies if the publisher is first party, third party reseller or third party agency.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property Quantity As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: Measure the quantity purchased or consumed.The amount of the meter used during the billing period.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ResellerMpnId As String

Docs.summary: MPNId for the reseller associated with the subscription.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ResellerName As String

Docs.summary: Reseller Name.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ReservationId As String

Docs.summary: ARM resource id of the reservation. Only applies to records relevant to reservations.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ReservationName As String

Docs.summary: User provided display name of the reservation. Last known name for a particular day is populated in the daily data. Only applies to records relevant to reservations.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ResourceGroup As String

Docs.summary: Name of the Azure resource group used for cohesive lifecycle management of resources.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ResourceLocation As String

Docs.summary: Name of the resource location.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ResourceLocationNormalized As String

Docs.summary: Resource Location Normalized.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ServiceFamily As String

Docs.summary: List the service family for the product purchased or charged (Example: Storage ; Compute).

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ServiceInfo1 As String

Docs.summary: Service-specific metadata.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ServiceInfo2 As String

Docs.summary: Legacy field with optional service-specific metadata.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ServicePeriodEndOn As Nullable(Of DateTimeOffset)

Docs.summary: End date for the period when the service usage was rated for charges. The prices for Azure services are determined based on the rating period.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property ServicePeriodStartOn As Nullable(Of DateTimeOffset)

Docs.summary: Start date for the rating period when the service usage was rated for charges. The prices for Azure services are determined for the rating period.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property SubscriptionGuid As String

Docs.summary: Unique Microsoft generated identifier for the Azure Subscription.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property SubscriptionName As String

Docs.summary: Name of the Azure Subscription.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property Term As String

Docs.summary: Term (in months). Displays the term for the validity of the offer. For example. In case of reserved instances it displays 12 months for yearly term of reserved instance. For one time purchases or recurring purchases, the terms displays 1 month; This is not applicable for Azure consumption.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property UnitOfMeasure As String

Docs.summary: Identifies the Unit that the service is charged in. For example, GB, hours, 10,000 s.

MemberSignature.Value: Public ReadOnly Property UnitPrice As Nullable(Of Decimal)

Docs.summary: Unit Price is the price applicable to you. (your EA or other contract price).
